🛍️ FakeStore E-commerce Scraper & Frontend Clone
This project is a full-stack demonstration that scrapes real-time e-commerce data from FakeStoreAPI using Python, and displays it in a modern, responsive frontend UI. It features live product filtering, search, metadata summary, and category-based browsing — built for learning, demo, or portfolio purposes.

📁 Project Structure
bash
Copy
Edit
.
├── main.py                # Python scraper for categories and products
├── products_data.csv      # Scraped product data (CSV)
├── ecommerce_data.json    # Scraped full data including metadata (JSON)
└── index.html             # Interactive frontend using HTML/CSS/JS
🚀 Features
🔍 Python Scraper (main.py)
Fetches product categories and product listings via REST API

Supports:

All products

Filter by category

JSON + CSV export

Includes timestamps and rating metadata

CLI-friendly and robust error handling

🌐 Frontend (HTML + JS)
Loads data from ecommerce_data.json

Category filter (e.g., electronics, jewelry)

Product search functionality

Real-time product count and metadata display

Responsive design with modern UI (no frameworks!)

